    • Constructor Detail

      • Account

        @Since(value="7.0")
public Account(Long accountID,
             String username,
             String status,
             Long[] volumes,
             Optional<CHAPSecret> initiatorSecret,
             Optional<CHAPSecret> targetSecret,
             Optional<Map<String,Object>> attributes)
        The object containing information about an account. This object only includes "configured" information about the account, not any runtime or usage information.
        Parameters:
        accountID - [required] Unique AccountID for the account.
        username - [required] User name for the account.
        status - [required] Current status of the account.
        volumes - [required] List of VolumeIDs for Volumes owned by this account.
        initiatorSecret - (optional) CHAP secret to use for the initiator.
        targetSecret - (optional) CHAP secret to use for the target (mutual CHAP authentication).
        attributes - (optional) List of Name/Value pairs in JSON object format.
        Since:
        7.0
